data.description: Lovely home in desirable Canyon de Flores neighborhood. Shows pride of ownership. Situated on a large, cul-de-sac lot, home features a large great room/dining combo, upgraded SS appliances, breakfast bar and interior storage in laundry room. Enjoy views of the Huachuca mountains from the front yard and summer evenings under the Ramada in the spacious back yard. Backyard is divided into separate sections for multi uses.
